1️⃣2️⃣ Big Data & Cloud Computing for Data Science
✅ Introduction to Big Data (Hadoop, Spark)
✅ Working with Apache Spark (PySpark)
✅ Cloud Services (AWS, Azure, GCP)
✅ Deploying Machine Learning Models in Cloud
________________________________________
1️⃣3️⃣ Model Deployment & MLOps
